videos.description: Kansas loses Austin Trice off the screen, and Trice makes them pay with the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sneed hits Trice for easy dunk) 2019/02/25

videos.headline: Sneed hits Trice for easy dunk

videos.description: Devon Dotson cuts through the Wildcats' defense and lays it in off the backboard while absorbing contact.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dotson slices through for and-1 layup) 2019/02/25

videos.headline: Dotson slices through for and-1 layup

videos.description: Mitch Lightfoot blocks a shot for the second straight possession, and Lightfoot channels Dikembe Mutombo with a finger wag.

videos.headline: Lightfoot does Mutombo finger wag after block

videos.description: Dedric Lawson's pass inside is poked away, but Lawson picks up the ball and hits a deep 2-pointer before the shot clock expires.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Lawson recovers to make deep jumper) 2019/02/25

videos.headline: Lawson recovers to make deep jumper
